Package: VARS
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given="Jincheng", family="Jiang", role = c("aut", "cre"), email="jc.j02@outlook.com")
Description: A simple package implementing reduced form VAR estimation (OLS and bayesian) method as well as structural form VAR identification. Currently supports recursive, sign and IV approach. Also, it provides VAR analysis tools like IRF, FEVD and HDC.
